The paper focuses on coded distributed computing (CDC) in heterogeneous computing systems, which involves aspects of distributed computing (cs.DC), information theory (cs.IT), control systems (cs.SY), networking and internet architecture (cs.NI), and robotics (cs.AR). Therefore, these are the most likely arXiv CS sub-categories for this paper, ordered from most to least likely.
